🗺️ DAY‑WISE CHEAP TRANSPORT PLAN

DAY 1 – Rishikesh → Guptkashi
Mode: UTC Govt Bus (BEST VALUE)

Board from: Rishikesh Bus Stand (early morning)
Route:
Rishikesh → Devprayag → Srinagar → Rudraprayag → Guptkashi
Time: 7–8 hrs
Cost: ₹500–₹700

✅ UTC buses run daily on this route during Char Dham season
✅ Cheapest long‑distance option in Uttarakhand [uttarakhandtrips.com], [travelvaidya.com]
Night: Budget guesthouse in Guptkashi (₹400–₹600)

DAY 2 – Guptkashi → Gaurikund → Kedarnath
Mode: Shared Taxi + Trek


Guptkashi → Sonprayag → Gaurikund

Shared Jeep: ₹50–₹100



Gaurikund → Kedarnath

Trek: 16 km (FREE)
